text: Hermetschwil-Staffeln was a municipality of the district of Bremgarten in the canton of Aargau in Switzerland. On 1 January 2014, the former municipality of Hermetschwil-Staffeln merged into the municipality of Bremgarten. ==Other websites== Category:Former municipalities of Aargau Category:2014 disestablishments in Europe Category:2010s disestablishments in Switzerland
